Title: Ruby Life Pools: Primalist Invasion
Description:
The Primalists have torn their way into our home. We were not prepared for such an intense attack... several got through.

One of our drakonid ventured in to follow them, but he has not reported his findings. I fear the worst.

I will stand guard. No more shall breach our walls while we draw breath, but you must stop those who made it inside.

Go!
ObjectivesText: Enter the Ruby Life Pools and stop the Primalist attack.
RewardText:
Our home will bear the wounds of this assault for years, but we are strong. We will endure... and the eggs we saved will bring about a bright future for us all.

Thank you.
